<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Nanga ka hi, Na aw nem chuh ka zai,
 Na hehpih thu eil hilh hi;
 Mahleh ginna khutin ei phawng dingin,
 Na kawm lam ei naihsak in.

[V2]
 Lalpa, Na kawm lam ei naihsak in,
 Kross-a Na thihna achun;
 Deihtak, Lalpa Na kawm lam ei naihsak in,
 Na-nak thiengtho liemna chu.

[V3]
 2. Na nasem di'n ei kawihchuom in Lalpa,
 Na thilbawl theihna mak chun;
 Kinem in ka thagau in en zing hen,
 Ka utna Nanga hi hen.

[V4]
 3. Kipahna thieng hun chawmcha mai ka neih,
 Na chutphah maah ka mang;
 Khupdina pauchamin Nang ka Pathien,
 Guol bangin ka hun ho hi.

[V5]
 4. Hehpihna thuk ka hetphak loh a um,
 Luipi lien chuh ka kan ma'n;
 Kipakna sang ka chan nailoh a um,
 Muonga, Nanga ka chawlh ma'n.</lyrics>
<title>DRAW ME NEARER</title>
</song>